## Modes

| Mode | Behavior | Agent streaming |
| ---- | --- | --- |
| `named` (default) | `cloudflared tunnel run --token` (token from encrypted config); stable `PublicBaseURL` | Yes |
| `none` | BYO `PublicBaseURL`; no cloudflared | Yes (if front door supports SSE) |
| `quick` | TryCloudflare ephemeral `*.trycloudflare.com` | **No** (no SSE; 200 in-flight cap) |

Secrets: tunnel token via `set-tunnel-token` Ôćĺ encrypted `config.json` only ÔÇö never env SoT, never slog raw token.

## Operations

- Download/cache cloudflared for darwin/linux amd64/arm64 under `{dataRoot}/bin/`.
- Supervise with `cloudflared tunnel --no-autoupdate run --token ÔÇŽ` ÔÇö **do not** use `service install` under our supervisor.
- Kill stale processes for same port (Unix `kill`).
- Health-probe public `/health`; restart with backoff on failure.
- Ephemeral Quick URLs Ôćĺ re-apply Cursor Base URL on change (T08).

### Quick Tunnel constraints

| Fact | Product impact |
| ---- | --- |
| Ephemeral `*.trycloudflare.com` | Re-apply Cursor Base URL on change |
| 200 in-flight cap Ôćĺ 429 | Heavy Agent sessions may fail |
| No SSE | Not Agent-ready ÔÇö use `named` or `none` |
| `~/.cloudflared/config.yaml` present | Quick Tunnel may refuse to start |

### `Ephemeral tunnel URL breaks Cursor`

| Symptom | Cause | Fix |
| ----- | ---- | ----- |
| Agent fails after gateway restart | trycloudflare.com URL rotated | Detect URL change; sync Cursor settings; notify user to retry |

### `Quick Tunnel streaming / SSE broken`

| Symptom | Cause | Fix |
| ----- | ---- | ----- |
| Stream fails via public URL; loopback OK | Quick Tunnels do not support SSE | Use `named` or `none` (BYO) |

### `Quick Tunnel won't start (config.yaml)`

| Symptom | Cause | Fix |
| ----- | ---- | ----- |
| cloudflared exits / no trycloudflare URL | `config.yaml` in `~/.cloudflared` | Rename/move file; retry or use `named` |

### `Named tunnel healthy but public 502/530`

| Symptom | Cause | Fix |
| ----- | ---- | ----- |
| `/health` fails on public hostname | No Published application route to gateway port | CF dashboard: hostname Ôćĺ `http://127.0.0.1:{port}` |

